<p class="subheadline">Hong Kong is home to over 50 species of coral reefs - more than all of the Caribbean combined.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p>We want to protect these reefs. How about you ?</p>
<p>Our plan how you can join our <strong>Ocean Youth Program</strong>:</p>
<ol>
<li>Screenings and Hands-on Workshops from now to April 2020. Screening the Netflix original documentary "Chasing Coral". Short panel discussion with guest and audience. Link: <a href="https://www.facebook.com/pg/makerbay/events" target="_blank" title="Makerbay Events" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://www.facebook.com/pg/makerbay/events</a></li>
<li>Open Water PADI Certification. DIY and STEAM Training from April - May 2020 (weekends)</li>
<li>
<p>Research &amp; Development from June - August 2020 (Summer Camp)</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p style="display: inline !important;"><strong>Please fill the short questionnaire and join our future events:</strong></p>
<p><strong><a href="https://frama.link/HKOceanYouth">https://frama.link/HKOceanYouth</a></strong></p>
