<p><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0716/8153/files/Capture_480x480.png?v=1573210016" alt="Coral riff mapping drone" width="480x480" height="480x480" /></p>
<p>Our goal now is to develop the next generation of the ocean drone which is:</p>
<ul>
<li>10x more accurate GPS positioning offer accurate positioning Laser quadrat provide scaling and depth information</li>
<li>50x faster Deploy quicker and cover larger area in a short time Highly repeatable using same mission waypoints</li>
<li>200x cheaper Modular design , adaptable to variety or propulsion &amp; frame material Combination of open source software/hardware &amp; local natural materials</li>
<li>10 x 50 x 200 = 100,000x better</li>
</ul>
